@startuml
!include theme.iuml
title 自适应模型调度状态图

[*] --> Balanced : 默认启用
[*] --> Manual : 调度关闭

state Manual as "manual\n保持用户配置"
state Balanced as "balanced\n默认平衡档"
state Quality as "quality\n高分辨率/精度优先"
state Anomaly as "anomaly\n小目标异常优先"
state Realtime as "realtime\n时延优先"
state Protect as "protect\n资源保护"

Manual --> Balanced : 管理员启用调度
Balanced --> Manual : 管理员关闭调度
Balanced --> Quality : 静态图或 GPU 余量充足
Balanced --> Anomaly : task_mode = road_anomaly
Balanced --> Realtime : 最近推理时延偏高
Balanced --> Protect : GPU/CPU/内存高压
Quality --> Realtime : 推理变慢
Quality --> Protect : 资源达到保护条件
Anomaly --> Realtime : 实时性不足
Anomaly --> Protect : 资源达到保护条件
Realtime --> Balanced : 负载恢复且满足滞回时间
Protect --> Balanced : 资源恢复且满足滞回时间
Balanced --> Balanced : 1.5s 资源缓存\n8s profile 滞回

note right of Protect
  降低输入尺寸与频率，
  必要时切换后备模型。
end note
note left of Quality
  提高输入尺寸，保留
  沙盘小目标识别能力。
end note
@enduml
